            },
            { 
                title: "The Grand Scale",
                targetId: 'poi-milkyway', 
                scale: 0.01, 
                text: "But to truly understand our place, we must pull back... Past the familiar glow of our galactic home..." 
            },
            { 
                title: "The Cosmic Web",
                targetId: 'poi-cosmicweb', 
                scale: 0.001, 
                text: "...to see the universe on its grandest scale. A cosmic web of structure, where galaxies themselves are but points of light. <span class='deep-dive-trigger' data-panel-id='panel-cosmic-web'>The Cosmic Web</span> is the true architecture of existence."
