            1.  **Noise Function:** The full GLSL implementation of a standard 3D Simplex noise algorithm is included. This adheres to the "no unproven external results" constraint by showing the complete algorithm, rather than treating it as a black box. It is supplemented with a Fractal Brownian Motion (FBM) function to create detailed, multi-layered cloud structures.
